{"tid":2261351,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊再破頂　高見604元　沈大師：技術位睇640蚊","createTime":"2020-10-28T08:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T10:24:24.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9974689782ab6317275e273954e693fbb2b50880","tid":2261351,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2929537/org/8318fa1ab14d0ecf98fecf25461aafde.jpg/tV6ft_x0exhE2O6Nnhx-shDnLeI8ocIjROm5V0TpuVc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2929537%2Forg%2F8318fa1ab14d0ecf98fecf25461aafde.jpg%2FtV6ft_x0exhE2O6Nnhx-shDnLeI8ocIjROm5V0TpuVc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4a54da9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「沈大師」沈振盈認為，技術上騰訊向上破位，估計可上望640元，如果11月12日公布第三季業績前股價繼續炒上，放榜後回調的機會偏高。至於「譚Sir」譚朗蔚則認為，短線上望620元，達標後再看680元。<br />\n<br />\n10月中騰訊突破前頂564元，今日成功衝破600元大關，再創上市新高，市值增至5.76萬億元。麥格理發表研究報告，根據螞蟻集團上市的估值，比較騰訊與螞蟻的支付業務，估計騰訊的盈利能力略勝一籌，故上調騰訊目標價，由797元升至815元，並重申「跑贏大市」評級。<br />\n<br />\n除了獲上調目標價外，騰訊業務亦有好消息。旗下新遊戲《天涯明月刀》於月中上線後，日前已成為中國App Store手遊收入榜的第一位；至於英雄聯盟手機版「英雄聯盟激鬥峽谷」，亦於明日起於多個地區公測。<br />\n<br />\n沈大師：ATMX有少少Over 有貨者放紙鳶<br />\n<br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈稱，本身騰訊技術上已破位向上，而大行報告所指的因素亦有助股價推升。沈大師認為目前是短線炒高，升勢有機會持續至下月12日，即騰訊公布第三季業績。但他估計升勢若持續至放榜，往後回調的機會卻大大增加。<br />\n<br />\n沈大師認為，技術位可上望640元，但建議投資者要有戒心，固然不能夠沽空騰訊，但亦要明白目前是短線投機炒作。「ATMX」除騰訊之外，其他的表現亦有板有眼，當中阿里巴巴（9988）已經破頂逼近310元。大師則認為4隻股票都偏貴，「有少少Over，美團更加係唔掂得」，即使他一直看好阿里巴巴，亦覺得估值過高，建議有貨者可「放紙鳶」，惟無貨者不必高追。"},{"pid":"42d0c9d9622eab736572f052d746634920bb07bc","tid":2261351,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"OK 沽"},{"pid":"9421ffdf7914166a3299e4d8bfe3528a96eda3fa","tid":2261351,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42d0c9d9622eab736572f052d746634920bb07bc","tid":2261351,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"OK 沽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"大膽!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b330cfb735bc0b8892cd7b9f4bf3f6dd51e9c94","tid":2261351,"uid":32352,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"請問技術位到底有咩技術？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedf00e6d97cd6dc4725397675eafdc537d178bc","tid":2261351,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"「有少少Over，美團更加係唔掂得」<br />\n<br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e842816a2b44b6011e8640b1bd52b6e621abb930","tid":2261351,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"沈大師咁講即係要走啦"},{"pid":"38e59e5470cbfca12345cadab5cb73e8923b6d14","tid":2261351,"uid":331469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"哦 64 大師犯左國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44491ec5a13d1e72d7ec2030b6b66fb56ea1d01a","tid":2261351,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e922d27df27f6cb8be8d1989ab607b5b9bfe2e","tid":2261351,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"當年大屍由未拆股前100蚊睇淡到家下睇好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9626254352611474f248b266480c2eb7ec6a6b3c","tid":2261351,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"騰訊一定大獲.GIF"},{"pid":"870acda439e73604fa8a09f16b6d63d0bb0cd734","tid":2261351,"uid":125888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"Cfu真係on99 又話$560唔值一定put<br />\n玩撚曬啦"},{"pid":"15d819bf758e65db7162307263cce3aea1851e2d","tid":2261351,"uid":18795,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{